Monica Dolan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monica_Dolan 0 Monica Margaret Dolan (born 2 March 1969) is a British actress. She won the BAFTA TV Award for Best Supporting Actress for playing Rosemary West in Appropriate Adult (2011). Monica_Margaret_Dolan ( born 2_March_1969 ) is a_British_actress . She won the_BAFTA_TV_Award for Best_Supporting_Actress for playing Rosemary_West in Appropriate_Adult_(_2011_) .
